<text><body>
<lb n="0030c10" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0030c11" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030c12" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030c13" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1040</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0030c14" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><note n="0030012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，【甲】三十帖策子第五</note>金剛頂降三世大儀軌法王教中
<lb n="0030c15" ed="T"/>觀自在菩薩心真言一切如來蓮
<lb n="0030c16" ed="T"/>花大曼<note n="0030013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">拏攞＝荼羅【甲】＊</note><app n="0030013"><lem wit="【大】">拏攞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">荼羅</rdg></app>品<note n="0030014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一卷〕－【甲】</note><app n="0030014"><lem wit="【大】">一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0030c17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0030c18" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0030015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔開府…智〕三十三字－【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="33" n="0030015"><lem wit="【大】">開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0030c19" ed="T"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒
<lb n="0030c20" ed="T"/>正號大廣智</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>大興善寺三藏沙<note n="0030016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">門＋（大廣智）【甲】</note><app n="0030016"><lem wit="【大】">門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">門大廣智</rdg></app>
<lb n="0030c21" ed="T"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0030c22" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT20p0030c2201">爾時觀自在菩薩摩訶薩。白佛言。世尊我欲
<lb n="0030c23" ed="T"/>於此降三世儀軌法王會中說自心真言。世
<lb n="0030c24" ed="T"/>尊若纔稱<note n="0030017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">說＝誦【甲】＊</note><app n="0030017"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">誦</rdg></app>一切如來。三昧現前一切怖畏
<lb n="0030c25" ed="T"/>厄難災障。及諸病惱皆得<note n="0030018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">消＝銷【甲】</note><app n="0030018"><lem wit="【大】">消</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">銷</rdg></app>滅。</p>
<lb n="0030c26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0030c2601">爾時薄伽梵。告觀自在菩薩言。善哉善哉汝
<lb n="0030c27" ed="T"/>應善說。時觀自在菩薩摩訶薩。承佛聖旨即
<lb n="0030c28" ed="T"/>說自心真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0030c29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0030c2901" cb:type="dharani">阿嚕<note n="0030019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（禮迦…引）十字＝（力）一字【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="10" n="0030019"><lem wit="【大】">禮迦<note place="inline">半</note>娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">力</rdg></app></p>
<pb n="0031a" xml:id="T20.1040.0031a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0031a01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0031a0101">適說此心真言時。一切如來從本剎土。雲集
<lb n="0031a02" ed="T"/>蘇<note n="0031001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">迷＝彌【甲】</note><app n="0031001"><lem wit="【大】">迷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">彌</rdg></app>盧頂毘盧遮那大會之中。圍遶觀自在
<lb n="0031a03" ed="T"/>菩薩摩訶薩復說自心真言大曼<app type="star" corresp="#0030013"><lem wit="【大】">拏攞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">荼羅</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0031a04" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0031a0401"><l>院位擘方設</l><l>內四角<note n="0031002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">四＝向【甲】</note><app n="0031002"><lem wit="【大】">四</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">向</rdg></app>門</l>
<lb n="0031a05" ed="T"/><l>善度最中央</l><l>井形<note n="0031003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">拼＝抨【甲】</note><app n="0031003"><lem wit="【大】">拼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">抨</rdg></app>四道</l>
<lb n="0031a06" ed="T"/><l>顯成於八位</l><l>分為八葉花</l>
<lb n="0031a07" ed="T"/><l>是色應用朱</l><l>中臺觀自在</l>
<lb n="0031a08" ed="T"/><l>於彼一一葉</l><l>圖畫大覺形</l>
<lb n="0031a09" ed="T"/><l>中院不為門</l><l>內外八線道</l>
<lb n="0031a10" ed="T"/><l>微妙建立已</l><l>阿闍梨當入</l>
<lb n="0031a11" ed="T"/><l>應對曼<app type="star" corresp="#0030013"><lem wit="【大】">拏攞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">荼羅</rdg></app></l><l>結大蓮花契</l>
<lb n="0031a12" ed="T"/><l>端身定支節</l><l>住於三摩地</l>
<lb n="0031a13" ed="T"/><l>次結盎俱施</l><l>奉請於聖者</l>
<lb n="0031a14" ed="T"/><l>若一切有情</l><l>入此曼<app type="star" corresp="#0030013"><lem wit="【大】">拏攞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">荼羅</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0031a15" ed="T"/><l>雖處於凡位</l><l>貪嗔罪垢滅</l>
<lb n="0031a16" ed="T"/><l>猶如於蓮花</l><l>不為水所著</l>
<lb n="0031a17" ed="T"/><l>勝生亦如是</l><l>不為欲所染</l></lg>
<lb n="0031a18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0031a1801">阿闍梨即以大蓮花印。屈進力度如鉤。請<note n="0031004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">觀＋（世）【甲】</note><app n="0031004"><lem wit="【大】">觀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">觀世</rdg></app>
<lb n="0031a19" ed="T"/>自在菩薩。蓮花鉤真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0031a2001" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline"><note n="0031005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">引＝一【甲】＊</note><app n="0031005"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">一</rdg></app></note>摩訶<note place="inline"><note n="0031006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">引＋（二）【甲】</note><app n="0031006"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">引二</rdg></app></note>跛<note n="0031007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">娜＝納【甲】＊</note><app n="0031007"><lem wit="【大】">娜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">納</rdg></app>摩<note place="inline">二<note n="0031008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">合＋（三）【甲】</note><app n="0031008"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">合三</rdg></app></note><note n="0031009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">吽＋（四）細註【甲】</note><app n="0031009"><lem wit="【大】">吽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">吽<note place="inline">四</note></rdg></app><note n="0031010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">惹＋（入五）細註【甲】</note><app n="0031010"><lem wit="【大】">惹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">惹<note place="inline">入五</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0031a21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0031a2101">即時觀自在菩薩便至道場現微妙色身。或
<lb n="0031a22" ed="T"/>放光明。阿闍梨次當如法引弟子入。是諸弟
<lb n="0031a23" ed="T"/>子應著白衣。復以白繒<note n="0031011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">掩＝帕【甲】</note><app n="0031011"><lem wit="【大】">掩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">帕</rdg></app>覆其<note n="0031012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">服＝眼【甲】</note><app n="0031012"><lem wit="【大】">服</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">眼</rdg></app>。又以淨
<lb n="0031a24" ed="T"/>帛纏繫其頭。既引入已而<app type="star" corresp="#0030017"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">誦</rdg></app>偈<note n="0031013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">言＝曰【甲】＊</note><app n="0031013"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">曰</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0031a25" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0031a2501"><l>猶如於蓮花</l><l>不為水所著</l>
<lb n="0031a26" ed="T"/><l>勝生亦如是</l><l>不為諸欲染</l></lg>
<lb n="0031a27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0031a2701">即應<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CBETA】【麗】">左<note type="cf1">K37n1366_p0260a16</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">在</rdg></app>手授與弟子蓮花。右手授與念珠。又
<lb n="0031a28" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0030017"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">誦</rdg></app>偈<app type="star" corresp="#0031013"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">曰</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0031a29" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT20p0031a2901"><l>諸佛大蓮花</l><l>於諸曼<app type="star" corresp="#0030013"><lem wit="【大】">拏攞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">荼羅</rdg></app></l>
<pb n="0031b" xml:id="T20.1040.0031b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0031b01" ed="T"/><l>最為其上首</l><l>常須分別思</l>
<lb n="0031b02" ed="T"/><l>身奉觀自在</l></lg>
<lb n="0031b03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0031b0301">然後教印及三摩地門。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0031b04" ed="T"/><cb:div type="pin"><cb:mulu level="1" n="2" type="品">心真言蓮花曼拏攞品</cb:mulu><head>心真言蓮花曼<app type="star" corresp="#0030013"><lem wit="【大】">拏攞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">荼羅</rdg></app>品</head>
<lb n="0031b05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0031b0501">復<note n="0031014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">次＝以【甲】</note><app n="0031014"><lem wit="【大】">次</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">以</rdg></app>如前建立曼<app type="star" corresp="#0030013"><lem wit="【大】">拏攞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">荼羅</rdg></app>。行者應坐中臺之
<lb n="0031b06" ed="T"/>上。入一切如來開敷蓮花三摩地。誦一洛叉
<lb n="0031b07" ed="T"/>即得觀自在身。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0031b08" ed="T"/><cb:div type="pin"><cb:mulu level="1" n="3" type="品">心真言三昧耶曼拏攞品</cb:mulu><head>心真言<note n="0031015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔三昧耶〕－【甲】</note><app n="0031015"><lem wit="【大】">三昧耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>曼<app type="star" corresp="#0030013"><lem wit="【大】">拏攞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">荼羅</rdg></app>品</head>
<lb n="0031b09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0031b0901">復以如前建立曼<app type="star" corresp="#0030013"><lem wit="【大】">拏攞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">荼羅</rdg></app>。應取一千蓮花。一花
<lb n="0031b10" ed="T"/>一誦安中臺以為奉獻。然後引弟子入告三
<lb n="0031b11" ed="T"/>昧耶言<note place="inline"><note n="0031016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">謂＝為【甲】＊</note><app n="0031016"><lem wit="【大】">謂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">為</rdg></app>諸欲清淨誓也</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0031b12" ed="T"/><cb:div type="pin"><cb:mulu level="1" n="4" type="品">羯磨曼拏攞品</cb:mulu><head>羯磨曼<app type="star" corresp="#0030013"><lem wit="【大】">拏攞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">荼羅</rdg></app>品</head>
<lb n="0031b13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0031b1301">復次如前建立曼<app type="star" corresp="#0030013"><lem wit="【大】">拏攞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">荼羅</rdg></app>。以四種供養。復次成
<lb n="0031b14" ed="T"/>就像法。於清淨絹㲲上。畫觀自在菩薩。坐蘇
<lb n="0031b15" ed="T"/>彌盧頂八佛圍遶。起白月一日於此像前。一
<lb n="0031b16" ed="T"/>切時無間斷入三摩地念誦。乃至畫像放光。
<lb n="0031b17" ed="T"/>於光明中流出觀自在菩薩及諸如來。入行
<lb n="0031b18" ed="T"/>者眉間灌頂之處。堅固而住。即時行者體同
<lb n="0031b19" ed="T"/>觀自在。剎那頃便見極樂世界。一切眾生皆
<lb n="0031b20" ed="T"/>見去時壽命無量。</p>
<lb n="0031b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0031b2101">我今又說成就之法。誦一洛叉。一切蓋障皆
<lb n="0031b22" ed="T"/>得清淨。誦二洛叉。所有五無間等一切諸罪
<lb n="0031b23" ed="T"/>盡滅無餘。誦三洛叉。一切福德來集。一切
<lb n="0031b24" ed="T"/>如來等備具。一切成智現前。</p>
<lb n="0031b25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0031b2501">復次若結大印<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0031016"><lem wit="【大】">謂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">為</rdg></app>五相成<note n="0031017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">就＝身【甲】</note><app n="0031017"><lem wit="【大】">就</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">身</rdg></app></note>誦洛叉數。經夜無限
<lb n="0031b26" ed="T"/>念誦。比至晨朝一切如來入行者心。即體同
<lb n="0031b27" ed="T"/>如來。若入於口即<note n="0031018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔體〕－【甲】</note><app n="0031018"><lem wit="【大】">體</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>同觀自在。</p>
<lb n="0031b28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0031b2801">復次成就事業。誦一遍護身。兩遍護他及城
<lb n="0031b29" ed="T"/>邑聚落。三遍<note n="0031019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即＝則【甲】</note><app n="0031019"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">則</rdg></app>能成辦一切事業。若阿尾捨
<pb n="0031c" xml:id="T20.1040.0031c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0031c01" ed="T"/>應燒檀香<note place="inline">加持八百遍爐中燒薰支分</note>若息諸鬼魅者。加<note n="0031020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">呬＝紇【甲】</note><app n="0031020"><lem wit="【大】">呬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">紇</rdg></app>
<lb n="0031c02" ed="T"/>唎<note n="0031021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合〕－【甲】</note><app n="0031021"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>字誦之。令一切有情<note n="0031022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（隨）＋順【甲】</note><app n="0031022"><lem wit="【大】">順</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">隨順</rdg></app>。加持金剛花
<lb n="0031c03" ed="T"/>與之<note place="inline">赤花代之</note>令惡心不動。以<note n="0031023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔白〕－【甲】</note><app n="0031023"><lem wit="【大】">白</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>土止息之<note place="inline">真言首加書朱
<lb n="0031c04" ed="T"/>書之名後即卷置一瓶之中以白土實<note n="0031024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">之＋（覆）【甲】</note><app n="0031024"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">之覆</rdg></app>安於一<note n="0031025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">坑＝瓶【甲】</note><app n="0031025"><lem wit="【大】">坑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">瓶</rdg></app>之中<note n="0031026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">後＝又【甲】</note><app n="0031026"><lem wit="【大】">後</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">又</rdg></app>土填之想室彼<note n="0031027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">兌＝瓮【甲】</note><app n="0031027"><lem wit="【大】">兌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">瓮</rdg></app>即安須彌山於其上下亦得耳</note>
<lb n="0031c05" ed="T"/>令悉底利敬愛。加持蘇末那花。與之伏從。又
<lb n="0031c06" ed="T"/>欲令一切禽獸隨處不動轉白芥子令一切禽
<lb n="0031c07" ed="T"/>獸不能動。加持白芥子遙向擲之。欲有所示
<lb n="0031c08" ed="T"/>現。加持孔雀尾遙轉。欲夢中知一切事。<note n="0031028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＋（時）【甲】</note><app n="0031028"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">三時</rdg></app>
<lb n="0031c09" ed="T"/>念誦其夜見<note n="0031029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔之〕－【甲】</note><app n="0031029"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。又欲除惡夢者。以油麻護
<lb n="0031c10" ed="T"/>摩。又欲止息口舌取雞翅翎護摩。若處子婆
<lb n="0031c11" ed="T"/>誐蘂淫女月帛護摩。悉<note n="0031030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嚩＝縛【甲】</note><app n="0031030"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">縛</rdg></app>始迦羅拏。若求一
<lb n="0031c12" ed="T"/>切事應廣供養觀自在。八日一日夜不食念
<lb n="0031c13" ed="T"/>誦滿一切願。又於觀自在菩薩前。三時時別
<lb n="0031c14" ed="T"/>誦三遍。滿三月菩薩滿其所願。又於佛像前
<lb n="0031c15" ed="T"/>三時時別誦三遍。滿三月佛滿其願。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0031c16" ed="T"/><cb:div type="pin"><cb:mulu level="1" n="5" type="品">印品</cb:mulu><head>印品</head>
<lb n="0031c17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0031c1701">合掌<note n="0031031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以＝已【甲】</note><app n="0031031"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">已</rdg></app>二水二風交地空各開竪。二火相合
<lb n="0031c18" ed="T"/>是根本印。芙蓉合掌是為大蓮花印。不易大
<lb n="0031c19" ed="T"/>蓮花開竪地空。是禳奪諸罪印。又外<note n="0031032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔叉〕－【甲】</note><app n="0031032"><lem wit="【大】">叉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>金剛
<lb n="0031c20" ed="T"/>縛。合二風如蓮花葉。二空竪相逼是三昧<note n="0031033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">印＝耶【甲】</note><app n="0031033"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">耶</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0031c21" ed="T"/>又分二<note n="0031034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">手＝羽【甲】</note><app n="0031034"><lem wit="【大】">手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">羽</rdg></app>作蓮花拳。便以慧拳旋繞定拳。作
<lb n="0031c22" ed="T"/>開八葉勢是羯磨印<note place="inline">請如來</note><note n="0031035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">呬唎＝紇利【甲】</note><app n="0031035"><lem wit="【大】">呬唎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">紇利</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>字觀於心
<lb n="0031c23" ed="T"/>月蓮。是法印。觀諸法如蓮花不著於水。諸法
<lb n="0031c24" ed="T"/>亦然不染欲等。是智印。蓮花阿闍梨。欲授弟
<lb n="0031c25" ed="T"/>子阿闍梨位。以蓮花授與弟子二掌中。又加
<lb n="0031c26" ed="T"/>持蓮花鬘一千八遍。繫弟子頭上。加持。</p>
<lb n="0031c27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0031c2701">真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0031c28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0031c2801" cb:type="dharani">唵<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0031005"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">一</rdg></app></note>跛<app type="star" corresp="#0031007"><lem wit="【大】">娜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">納</rdg></app>麼<note place="inline">二合</note>麼<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0031036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">攞＝羅【甲】</note><app n="0031036"><lem wit="【大】">攞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">羅</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>鼻詵<note n="0031037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">左路引計濕＝者三魯計失【甲】</note><app n="0031037"><lem wit="【大】">左路<note place="inline">引</note>計
<lb n="0031c29" ed="T"/>濕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">者三魯計失</rdg></app>嚩<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0031038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">囉＋（四）細註【甲】</note><app n="0031038"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囉<note place="inline">四</note></rdg></app>數<note n="0031039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">索＋（五）細註【甲】</note><app n="0031039"><lem wit="【大】">索</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">索<note place="inline">五</note></rdg></app></p>
<pb n="0032a" xml:id="T20.1040.0032a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0032a01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0032a0101">由是得為蓮花部中阿闍梨。我今說蓮花部
<lb n="0032a02" ed="T"/>修行禁戒儀。則先供養觀自在菩薩。應服一
<lb n="0032a03" ed="T"/>掬遇牟怛囉若少分摩夷。即一切清淨。然觀
<lb n="0032a04" ed="T"/>自身作觀自在菩薩。日誦一千遍乃至七日。
<lb n="0032a05" ed="T"/>禁戒得成就。從此已後一切食一切處作。皆
<lb n="0032a06" ed="T"/>不為污染。我今說普通一切供養儀。則二<note n="0032001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔手〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0032001"><lem wit="【大】">手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0032a07" ed="T"/>為金剛拳。各安於腰側。向左小低頭。是為恭
<lb n="0032a08" ed="T"/>敬禮。又二<app type="star" corresp="#0032001"><lem wit="【大】">手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>從額分向後繫鬘勢。歷度下垂
<lb n="0032a09" ed="T"/>帶。是為獻花鬘。又二<app type="star" corresp="#0032001"><lem wit="【大】">手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>從於臍漸上至口
<lb n="0032a10" ed="T"/>寫。是為獻歌詠。又二<app type="star" corresp="#0032001"><lem wit="【大】">手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>從<note n="0032002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔口〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032002"><lem wit="【大】">口</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>檀慧歷展相
<lb n="0032a11" ed="T"/>旋遶上頂虛合掌。是獻金剛舞。由是供養如
<lb n="0032a12" ed="T"/>來位尚不難得。況餘悉地。何以故。一切樂不
<lb n="0032a13" ed="T"/>如此金剛薩埵故。</p>
<lb n="0032a14" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>金剛頂<note n="0032003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔經〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032003"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>降三世<note n="0032004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔大〕－【甲】</note><app n="0032004"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>儀軌法<note n="0032005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔王教…卷〕二十四字－【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="24" n="0032005"><lem wit="【大】">王教中觀自
<lb n="0032a15" ed="T"/>在菩薩心真言一切如來蓮花大曼拏攞品一
<lb n="0032a16" ed="T"/>卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>